snippet.textDisplay:
The annual Flushing Lunar New Year parade was held on Saturday, January 25, 2020, in Queens, New York.

Falun Dafa practitioners were invited to attend the parade by event organizers again this year. They had a large group of several hundred practitioners and many different sections and themes. Practitioners also handed out information about the meditation practice to the spectators who lined the streets.
